                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Zend_File does not know about Zend_Form_Element.\r\nWhen Zend_Form says that there is an file element which has to be validated Zend_File tries to validate it (as it is called by Zend_Form).\r\n\r\nMy expectation is that validations should NOT BE PROCESSED\/DONE for disabled elements.\r\nTherefor I don't see this as failure from Zend_File but from Zend_Form which should not try to validate an disabled element.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
